graph TD
    Start([Start: Recruiter sends a chat message])
    HTTP[POST /api/v1/intents/extract<br/>messages, draft, user_message]
    AuthCheck{Bearer JWT valid?}
    Auth401[Return 401 unauthorized]
    InputCheck{user_message present?<br/><= 4000 chars?}
    Input400[Return 400 user_message_required<br/>or message_too_long]
    Truncate[Truncate history to last 20 turns]
    BuildReq[Build Messages API request:<br/>cached system prompt + propose_draft tool<br/>+ history + draft state + user_message]
    LLMCall[Call Claude with tool_choice=propose_draft]
    LLMOK{Upstream OK?}
    LLM503[Return 503 llm_unavailable<br/>FE shows offline banner; form still editable]
    Parse[Parse tool_use input → DraftPatch + reply + complete + missing]
    Validate[Domain validation:<br/>drop invalid work_mode/priority/<br/>headcount/years range/empty skills<br/>into warnings]
    Resp[Return 200 with reply + sparse patch<br/>+ complete + missing + warnings]
    FEMerge[FE merges patch into draft<br/>appends reply to messages<br/>renders warnings as soft amber chip]
    End([End: Draft updated; recruiter can keep chatting<br/>or click Create Draft Intent])

    Start --> HTTP
    HTTP --> AuthCheck
    AuthCheck -->|No| Auth401
    AuthCheck -->|Yes| InputCheck
    InputCheck -->|No| Input400
    InputCheck -->|Yes| Truncate
    Truncate --> BuildReq
    BuildReq --> LLMCall
    LLMCall --> LLMOK
    LLMOK -->|No| LLM503
    LLMOK -->|Yes| Parse
    Parse --> Validate
    Validate --> Resp
    Resp --> FEMerge
    FEMerge --> End
